platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Hipster Whale's Apple Design Awardwinning game takes a timeless arcade formulacross a road bustling with traffic and deadly obstaclesand transforms it into an adorable infinite runner. As you progress, youll unlock new characters with wildly diverse looks and effects. Theres a teeny-tiny flea, an emo goose, and even a few characters from other gameslike Epoch, who sprays cars with blocky bullets. The creativity and care put into Crossy Roads wacky world are unmistakable.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: These games are tough, but without a challenge, what's the point of ruling leaderboards?
